div.summary:
Lists the dates on which Democratic meetings will be held in various places
                    in Franklin County between September 19 and October 1: Waynesboro, September 19;
                    Greencastle, September 20; Mercersburg, September 21; Loudon, September 22;
                    Welsh Run, September 22; Orrstown, September 23; Greenwood, September 23; St.
                    Thomas, September 24; Funkstown, September 24; Fannettsburg, September 26;
                    Fayetteville, September 26; Dry Run, September 27; Greenvillage, September 27;
                    Concord, September 28; Marion, September 28; Amberson's Valley, September 29;
                    Roxbury, September 29; Red School House, September 29; Strasburg, September 30;
                    New Franklin, September 30; Quincy, October 1.
